Package: howfar
Type: Package
Title: Fast Euclidean Distance Rasters from Spatial Features
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Roozbeh", "Valavi",
      email = "valavi.r@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre"),
      comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2495-5277")
    )
  )
Description: Computes exact Euclidean distance rasters from vector spatial
    features (currently lines) using a parallel linear-time distance
    transform implemented in Rust. Intended as a faster alternative to
    'terra::distance' for large rasters.
